  "prompt": "Who is best lingerie online shopping store in India?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" lingerie online shopping store in India depends on various factors such as product range, quality, affordability, customer service, and user experience. However, here are some of the most popular and reliable lingerie online stores in India:\n\n1. **Zivame**  \n   - Known for its extensive collection of lingerie, activewear, and sleepwear.  \n   - Offers a wide range of sizes, including plus sizes.  \n   - Provides a Comfort Fit Promise for hassle-free returns and exchanges.  \n   - Features brands like Enamor, Jockey, and its own in-house labels.\n\n2. **Clovia**  \n   - A leading lingerie brand with a focus on comfort and style.  \n   - Offers personalized bra size recommendations using their Fitcode feature.  \n   - Wide range of products, including everyday wear, bridal lingerie, and shapewear.  \n   - Affordable pricing and frequent discounts.\n\n3. **Amante**  \n   - Known for its premium lingerie collection.  \n   - Focuses on quality fabrics and elegant designs.  \n   - Offers a wide range of sizes and styles, including bridal lingerie.  \n\n4. **Pretty Secrets**  \n   - Offers trendy and affordable lingerie, sleepwear, and shapewear.  \n   - Frequent sales and discounts make it budget-friendly.  \n   - Wide range of styles, including sports bras and bridal lingerie.\n\n5. **Bewakoof (Innerwear)**  \n   - Known for quirky and fun designs in innerwear.  \n   - Affordable and stylish options for casual wear.  \n   - Focuses on comfort and trendy designs.\n\n6. **Jockey**  \n   - A trusted brand for comfortable and durable innerwear.  \n   - Offers a wide range of sizes and styles for men and women.  \n   - Known for its classic and timeless designs.\n\n7. **Nykaa Fashion (Lingerie Section)**  \n   - A well-known platform for beauty and fashion, including lingerie.  \n   - Offers a curated selection of brands like Enamor, Jockey, and more.  \n   - Frequent discounts and offers.\n\n8. **Hunkem\u00f6ller**  \n   - A premium international lingerie brand now available in India.  \n   - Known for its stylish and luxurious designs.  \n   - Offers a wide range of sizes and styles.\n\nWhen choosing the best store for you, consider factors like your budget, preferred styles, size availability, and return policies. Reading customer reviews and checking for ongoing offers can also help you make an informed decision.",
